{"tid":2171546,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"確診前踩三場騷 猛人中招  慶回歸毒舞后 引爆江湖群組","createTime":"2020-08-24T04:22:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T03:45:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b0f043a35d566bcbdf064c75b8dc74d8bea12537","tid":2171546,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T04:22:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200824/DWP5DDQOTRGHLE5GIOTQTB4744/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200824%2FDWP5DDQOTRGHLE5GIOTQTB4744%2F&d=aCvg504CNSeS5FxaNurzsllQFaTeS91CmK6iy9gpT9M%3D&h=8e21fa00\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200824%2FDWP5DDQOTRGHLE5GIOTQTB4744%2F&h=58b7b9bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200824/DWP5DDQOTRGHLE5GIOTQTB4744/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n <br />\n確診前踩三場騷 猛人中招 <br />\n慶回歸毒舞后 引爆江湖群組<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】武肺第三波疫情中，累計74人確診的貨櫃碼頭群組，當局調查發現，首宗患者來自稻香慶回歸晚宴。本報經一個月追查慶回歸群組，被指為播毒者之一的勁舞綠衣姐，確診前五日唱足三場騷，不但觸發大媽群組，更在江湖壽宴表演後，多名猛人中招，釀成一個不在官方紀錄上的「江湖群組」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：歌友染疫 與麥德羅共用一咪<br />\n<br />\n記者：郭美華 張 軍 黃麗英<br />\n<br />\n引爆這場武肺災難，就是7月9日旺角稻香集團酒樓一個「慶回歸創輝煌歌舞晚會」，有指當晚筵開約30席，全場逼爆近300人，大媽們除罩亂舞，疑為播毒元凶，其後引發多個大型。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：《隆重登場》大媽：播疫唔光彩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/sazp5UelIlRYIULRxMIG-8jCT4s=/883x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HLR7ISVYPFFTLEFQJAPOGERHAY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fsazp5UelIlRYIULRxMIG-8jCT4s%3D%2F883x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHLR7ISVYPFFTLEFQJAPOGERHAY.jpg&h=a35bacaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■現年39歲的小雪BB（藝名）在業餘歌手界頗有名氣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩兒及女傭確診 鄰居驚惶<br />\n<br />\n本報追查發現，綠衣姐正是第1820號患者，藝名小雪BB，39歲，在業餘歌手界頗有名氣，她上月16日發病，19日確診，與多個爆疫群組患者有流行病學關連，包括葵芳新都會潮庭群組、荔景紀律部隊群組等，她家中兩名分別6歲及7歲的兒子，亦於7月21日確診，經治療後已出院，惟小雪染病逾一個月，終於上周四康復出院。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TOwSZJ-MGYM4nwngAmMuyczsb2s=/1684x6985/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6LJ4FCALBBEMBCPHRF4SR5EO54.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTOwSZJ-MGYM4nwngAmMuyczsb2s%3D%2F1684x6985%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6LJ4FCALBBEMBCPHRF4SR5EO54.gif&h=78115e13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n手機用戶請按此放大圖表<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://staticarc.appledaily.hk/daily/local/20200824/a6-hkg_box.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstaticarc.appledaily.hk%2Fdaily%2Flocal%2F20200824%2Fa6-hkg_box.gif&h=25fde086&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記者到其所住的廣興大廈了解，有鄰居透露小雪一家中招，包括其女傭，「嗰幾日搞到我哋要經上一層或下一層上落！」鄰居為。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另一鄰居坦言，以往經常見小雪出入，「成日唱歌表演，扮到好靚！」住上層的小雪友人直言，早前她留院期間因屋內無人，疑。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n不過，記者追蹤她發病前的行蹤，發現她在7月7日至11日五天內至少出席。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事後向同場歌友瞞疫<br />\n<br />\n不過，小雪卻疑隱瞞病情，向同場多名歌友發訊息稱自己檢測是陰性，又上載直播片，留言稱：「乖乖留在家中做主播練歌，齊。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n其中於7月11日參與「抗疫齊心詠香江網上音樂會」的歌手五毫子表示，當日曾與小雪同場，雖然大家輪流獻唱，但都驚中招：「當日晚會海報、視頻都見到小雪，我哋嘅音樂會同呢個晚會只差兩日，所以大家都好緊張。」。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n日前記者再到訪小雪住所，兒子透露母親仍未出院，其後小雪主動來電否認中招，「我冇必要同你講，呢啲係我私隱。」被指隱瞞確診做法自私，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n葵青區議員郭子健表示，有長亨邨街坊與小雪一同出席慶回歸晚會後確診，連。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"019dd2682ef601aa5dd68b055100b6cb6d6c67ea","tid":2171546,"uid":48360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T03:43:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote> <br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/sazp5UelIlRYIULRxMIG-8jCT4s=/883x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HLR7ISVYPFFTLEFQJAPOGERHAY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fsazp5UelIlRYIULRxMIG-8jCT4s%3D%2F883x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHLR7ISVYPFFTLEFQJAPOGERHAY.jpg&h=a35bacaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■現年39歲的小雪BB（藝名）在業餘歌手界頗有名氣。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好撚娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ad97a86fea7484f0755add3b8ff4a190c5fc7c6","tid":2171546,"uid":129169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T03:45:00.000Z","msg":"有名氣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做雞都會窮啦下化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成浸北姑徐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}